description: Based on the life of poet Jimmy Santiago Baca, this Taylor Hackford-directed story centers on the paths of three members of an East Los Angles gang.  Half brothers Paco and Cruz and their cousin Miklo cope with the lways violence and drugs have ruined their lives--Miklo goes to San Quentin prison, Cruz shows talent as an artist but is ruled by a heroin addiction, and Paco joins the police department, making enemies with Miklo upon his release.
